From 0a933b9fb0705e162496df2d85268f5a892015d0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Chris Friedt <chris@fr4.co>
Date: Sat, 25 Apr 2026 17:38:17 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] kernel: migrate dynamic thread stack APIs to SYS_THREAD

Move k_thread_stack_alloc()/k_thread_stack_free() implementations from
kernel/dynamic.c into lib/os/thread.c so they use the SYS_THREAD
elastipool-backed stack pool.

As part of this migration:
- remove kernel/dynamic.c and kernel/dynamic_disabled.c
- stop building dynamic.c variants from kernel/CMakeLists.txt
- mark CONFIG_DYNAMIC_THREAD and related knobs deprecated
- update dynamic_thread_stack tests to use CONFIG_SYS_THREAD settings

Signed-off-by: Friedt Professional Engineering Services, Inc
---
 kernel/CMakeLists.txt                         |   6 -
 kernel/Kconfig                                |   6 +-
 kernel/dynamic.c                              | 175 ------------------
 kernel/dynamic_disabled.c                     |  25 ---
 lib/os/thread.c                               |  94 ++++++++++
 .../threads/dynamic_thread_stack/prj.conf     |  14 +-
 .../threads/dynamic_thread_stack/src/main.c   |  79 +++-----
 .../dynamic_thread_stack/testcase.yaml        |  62 +------
 8 files changed, 139 insertions(+), 322 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 kernel/dynamic.c
 delete mode 100644 kernel/dynamic_disabled.c

